Sanguisorba minor

   [9535.jpg]
   Authority Scop.
   Family Magnoliopsida:Rosidae:Rosales:Rosaceae
   Synonyms
   Common names garden burnet, salad burnet, toper's-plant, pimpinela de
   Italia
   Editor
   Ecocrop code 9535

   Notes
   SOURCES
   Prakash V 1990 pp 23 [TEXT, USE]
   Roecklein J 1987 pp 509 [USE, DEP, DRA, LIMITS, PH]
   Duke J 1975 pp 26 [PH, RAIN, TEMP]
   GROWING PERIOD
   Perennial herb. (GMIN estimated by the compiler).
   COMMON NAMES
   Burnet.
   FURTHER INF
   Scientific synonym: Poterium sanguisorba. The plant can reach 60 cm in
   height. Burnet can be found at elevations up to 2300 m.

   Sources

   FAO - Food and Agriculture Organization of the UN - Helping to build a
   world without hunger
